Text.string: Woof! That didn't go good for 'em.
Looks like I'm goin' another round!
Heal up! I need you alive!
Don't say I never gave you nothin'.
Nah uh, you're not going down today!
Don't be a wimp! Move up!
C'mere and get what's comin' to ya!
Take that! And that! AND THAT ONE!
I call dibs on that one!
I'm okay, I'm okay... ugh. I'm not okay.
Ha! I knew I'd be back!
Do I gotta do everything around here?!
Don't stop shootin'! I got ya!
Come on, come on. Up with ya!
Now back to the fight with ya!
Ain't lettin' you die on me today!
